===============================================================================
class-field-edges
===============================================================================
Test that edges are drawn from classes to their field types.
lang: typescript

--- file: sample/src/lib.ts ---

class Address {
    street: string;
    city: string;
}

class Person {
    name: string;
    home: Address;
}

--- expect:arch-graph ---
